        "content": {
          "content_type": "text",
          "parts": [
            "Here’s a polished dissertation-style acknowledgement section in LaTeX format. It thanks your advisor, committee, lab members, family, and friends in a professional yet warm tone:  \n\n```latex\n\\chapter*{Acknowledgements}\n\\addcontentsline{toc}{chapter}{Acknowledgements}\n\nI would like to express my deepest gratitude to my advisor, Prof.~Kate Isaacs, for her invaluable guidance, patience, and encouragement throughout my doctoral journey. Her insight, mentorship, and unwavering support have profoundly shaped not only this dissertation but also my approach to research and scholarship.\n\nI am also thankful to the members of my supervisory committee for their constructive feedback, thoughtful questions, and continuous support. Their expertise and advice have been instrumental in refining the direction and contributions of this work.\n\nI wish to extend my appreciation to the members of our research lab for creating a collaborative and stimulating environment. The many discussions, brainstorming sessions, and shared challenges have enriched my research experience and made this journey far more rewarding.\n\nMy heartfelt thanks go to my family, whose unconditional love, sacrifices, and belief in me provided the foundation for all my endeavors. Their support has been my greatest source of strength.\n\nFinally, I am grateful to my friends, who offered encouragement, understanding, and much-needed laughter along the way. Their presence has made this journey not only possible but also enjoyable.\n\nTo all who have contributed to this work, directly or indirectly, I extend my sincere appreciation.\n```\n\nDo you want me to make it **more formal and concise** (like typical academic dissertations), or **more personal and narrative** (with a warmer, more heartfelt tone)?"
          ]
        },
